<node id="B人員">
  <data key="d0">B人員</data>
  <data key="d1">處理工程師</data>
  <data key="d2">B人員 is a processing engineer responsible for conducting maintenance work and ensuring the stability of systems provided to C客户. The role includes various tasks related to system maintenance, such as addressing anomalies, performing updates, and implementing necessary security patches. Specifically, B人员 conducts multiple maintenance activities like GeoDB updates, GitLab upgrades, construction of record review dashboards for AI websites, patching VMware Tools vulnerabilities, modifying IP whitelist settings, updating Splunk驻点服务, adjusting alarm syntax, and managing F5VPN specific user connection logs.

B人員 is dedicated to maintaining system integrity and ensuring smooth operations through a variety of technical tasks and updates. For example, on January 5, 2026, B人员 performed maintenance work including the Splunk驻点 service. On October 20, 2025, from 11:00 to 16:00, B人員 conducted a specific set of maintenance activities for C客户. These responsibilities highlight the comprehensive nature of the tasks undertaken by B人员, which are crucial for keeping systems up-to-date and secure.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員是進行維護工作的處理工程師。&lt;SEP&gt;B人員與C人員共同參與了維護工作，一起解決Splunk異常狀況。&lt;SEP&gt;B人員為C客戶提供維護服務，主要進行GeoDB更新、漏洞修補等工作。&lt;SEP&gt;B人員是進行維護工作的處理工程師。&lt;SEP&gt;進行維護工作的處理工程師。</data>
