<edge source="維護紀錄" target="伺服器">
  <data key="d7">16.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(伺服器, 維護紀錄) refers to the maintenance records of a server that document various aspects related to its performance and operational status. These records include detailed information about efficiency checks conducted as part of routine maintenance activities, ensuring all parameters fall within normal ranges and confirming correct operation of the server. Maintenance logs also provide assessments of the server’s current condition, consistently noting its normal performance status.

The descriptions detail specific instances where issues on a Splunk Indexer server were diagnosed and temporarily resolved during the maintenance process. Optimization recommendations are provided based on an analysis of the server's performance metrics and authorized usage limits, particularly for F customers. The records include evaluations of space usage on servers such as IDX01, IDX02, and IDX03, along with related recommendation measures.

Furthermore, the (伺服器, 維護紀錄) includes detailed assessments of server performance reports and system optimization suggestions. Specific maintenance actions are documented, such as addressing problems on the FWD02 server and proposing updates based on performance evaluations. During these maintenance processes, the server's efficiency is assessed, and recommendations for improvements are made to enhance functionality.

Overall, (伺服器, 維護紀錄) serves as a comprehensive documentation tool that supports ongoing monitoring and enhancement of server functionality by providing detailed records of assessments, optimizations, and resolutions related to various servers.&lt;SEP&gt;伺服器的效能情況被包含在維護紀錄中，確認其正常運行。</data>
  <data key="d9">優化建議,問題報告,問題診斷,報告,建議,性能評估,授權用量,措施建議,故障修復,效能報告,效能檢查,效能評估,檢查對象,檢查結果,檢查項目,狀態報告,系統效能,系統檢視,維護活動,處理方案,設備檢查,設備狀態,設備監控,評估,評估對象</data>
