<edge source="維護紀錄" target="B客戶">
  <data key="d7">16.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(B客戶, 維護紀錄) is a relationship characterized by the meticulous recording and documentation of maintenance work performed for B客户. These records are specifically designed to meet the needs and requirements set forth by B客户, detailing every aspect of system maintenance conducted on their behalf by A personnel. The primary focus of these documents includes comprehensive descriptions of all maintenance tasks, issues encountered during service delivery, and the corresponding measures taken to address these problems.

The (B客戶, 維護紀錄) relationship covers a wide range of activities aimed at improving B客户的 system performance and security. These records document multiple maintenance operations and their outcomes in detail. Each record is generated based on the specific needs identified by B客户, leading to the initiation and execution of corresponding maintenance work.

For instance, one notable entry in these records details all maintenance work matters carried out on November 18, 2025. This comprehensive documentation not only covers the specifics of each maintenance task but also provides broader context about customer service interactions and the performance of handling engineers responsible for executing the maintenance work.

Overall, (B客戶, 維護紀錄) ensures a thorough and detailed record-keeping process that is integral to maintaining B客户的 system integrity and addressing their specific needs effectively.&lt;SEP&gt;B客戶有一筆由處理工程師A人員和C人員進行的維護紀錄。</data>
