<edge source="維護紀錄" target="C人員">
  <data key="d7">37.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(C人員, 維護紀錄) refers to the relationship where C personnel are responsible for maintaining and updating records of maintenance activities related to E客户. In this role, C人员 serve as both the creator and executor of these maintenance records, documenting their activities and resolving problems encountered during the process. They ensure transparency and accountability in service delivery by meticulously recording all actions taken, including the completion of assigned tasks and addressing customer needs.

C人員 perform various specific operations such as completing maintenance reports and confirming data accuracy. For instance, they document efforts in resolving issues like websense断行问题 within the maintenance record. Their responsibilities include performing the actual work described in the maintenance records and ensuring that all relevant details are accurately recorded for future reference. Additionally, C人员 often collaborate with A人员 to carry out these tasks jointly.

C人員's duties also involve proposing system optimization suggestions while reworking previous CSR content as part of their responsibilities. The maintenance record provides detailed documentation of all actions taken by C人员 during the work, covering both execution and reporting phases. Their responsibilities encompass executing necessary tasks and meticulously recording activities in the maintenance record to ensure comprehensive coverage of the entire maintenance process.

Specifically, C人員 are involved in completing maintenance reports, confirming data accuracy, resolving issues, and proposing system improvements. They participate in E客户's maintenance work and document their actions throughout a specified time range. For example, they completed A客户的 maintenance needs, including upgrading Splunk versions on multiple servers. Moreover, C人员 collaborate with A人员 to complete parts of the maintenance tasks recorded in the records.

C人員 are also responsible for executing the specific work matters described in the maintenance record and performing related handling actions. They provide detailed documentation of handling actions and temporary solutions for service anomalies involving C客户. Additionally, they participate in maintenance work alongside A人员, assisting them in solving problems and completing relevant tasks.

In summary, C人員 play a pivotal role by both carrying out necessary tasks and meticulously recording these activities in the maintenance record to ensure that all aspects of the service delivery are transparent and accountable to E客戶. Their responsibilities include upgrading software versions like Splunk on multiple servers, ensuring data accuracy, resolving issues promptly, and collaborating with A人员 to address customer needs comprehensively.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員負責進行了一筆關於E客戶的維護紀錄。</data>
