<edge source="維護紀錄" target="C客戶">
  <data key="d7">10.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(C客戶, 維護紀錄) is a record detailing the maintenance services provided to C客戶. This documentation comprehensively outlines the status and actions taken during various maintenance activities performed for C客戶. The maintenance work involves detailed descriptions of the content and progress of related maintenance tasks carried out by designated personnel such as B人员. Specifically, it includes information about the maintenance activities conducted on January 19, 2026, by B人员. This record serves to maintain a clear account of all maintenance procedures and their outcomes for C客戶's systems.&lt;SEP&gt;維護紀錄是針對C客戶的維護需求而產生的。&lt;SEP&gt;維護紀錄是為C客戶進行的一次維護工作。</data>
