<edge source="C客戶" target="B人員">
  <data key="d7">10.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(B人員, C客戶) refers to a relationship where B personnel provide maintenance services for C customers. This includes handling various issues and performing multiple tasks related to software updates, security patches, and specific maintenance steps such as updating geodb, restoring database IOC pages, adjusting HTTP external data transmission reports, adding URLs under surveillance, resolving Splunk anomalies, and other detailed work contents.

B人員 are responsible for conducting comprehensive maintenance activities that cover a wide range of responsibilities including but not limited to software updates, security fixes, data recovery tasks, and addressing specific issues such as Splunk malfunctions. These services aim to ensure the smooth operation and optimal performance of systems used by C客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員為C客戶提供了一筆維護紀錄。&lt;SEP&gt;處理工程師B人員為客戶C客戶提供維護服務。</data>
  <data key="d9">客戶支持,客戶服務,客戶關係,支持,服務,服務提供,維護,維護工作,維護活動,維護責任,維護需求</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-ab226f704fc1b4d45dd06222f40cb39f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d3d3acb3c191c9e65fac21b5ed9284f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c1fca5402ff2eb1c53222e1d4db282a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f6caccf00501b5f4caf06dcfc047ae9e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0b9e37e8f7e8a98183b1724c16ce814a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e7cec156f57837e8d25cbe83a6db45f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f23819b8640c43571e6e9b3e4098e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-068ca517cbebf973fd4089bd45ef615c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cdd29ae3537f38a27c3848632ad51359&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8ec2739edb4ee1ccc4cf68534e90be5</data>
